15
00:01:23,540 --> 00:01:28,140
♪Stories linger warmly,
with a faint sense of nostalgia♪

16
00:01:28,420 --> 00:01:34,940
♪Stories with a faint sense
of nostalgia♪

17
00:01:34,940 --> 00:01:36,940
[Second Chance Romance]

18
00:01:37,020 --> 00:01:39,940
[Episode 8]

19
00:01:49,380 --> 00:01:49,900
Mr. Gao.

20
00:01:52,100 --> 00:01:52,740
Mr. Gao,

21
00:01:53,060 --> 00:01:54,180
what's up?

22
00:01:54,220 --> 00:01:55,020
Where is your director?

23
00:01:55,380 --> 00:01:56,580
He has off work.

24
00:01:56,580 --> 00:01:58,420
Please come back tomorrow
during the day.

25
00:01:58,580 --> 00:01:59,220
Off work?

26
00:02:02,820 --> 00:02:03,420
Who are you?

27
00:02:03,420 --> 00:02:04,180
I've not seen you

28
00:02:04,180 --> 00:02:04,700
before.

29
00:02:05,620 --> 00:02:07,820
I'm Shi Wei from the Finance Department.

30
00:02:08,060 --> 00:02:08,940
I look forward to your guidance.

31
00:02:09,140 --> 00:02:09,540
Okay.

32
00:02:10,820 --> 00:02:11,700
Transfer the money to me.

33
00:02:11,860 --> 00:02:12,580
I need it urgently.

34
00:02:14,900 --> 00:02:17,340
I, I can't make that decision.

35
00:02:17,980 --> 00:02:18,820
Can't make the decision?

36
00:02:19,660 --> 00:02:20,620
I can't.

37
00:02:20,940 --> 00:02:22,380
You're so pretty and you can't?

38
00:02:25,300 --> 00:02:27,020
I, I really can't.

39
00:02:27,260 --> 00:02:28,740
Please come back tomorrow.

40
00:02:31,180 --> 00:02:31,860
I understand.

41
00:02:31,860 --> 00:02:32,740
You have procedures.

42
00:02:33,020 --> 00:02:34,340
But Ms. Gao has approved it.

43
00:02:35,780 --> 00:02:36,340
Come on.

44
00:02:37,380 --> 00:02:37,780
Come here.

45
00:02:41,340 --> 00:02:42,220
Let me teach you.

46
00:02:43,020 --> 00:02:43,620
Put your hand

47
00:02:43,700 --> 00:02:44,780
right here.

48
00:02:47,300 --> 00:02:48,100
Click it.

49
00:02:48,900 --> 00:02:49,740
See? That's it!

50
00:02:53,060 --> 00:02:54,420
No, this won't work.

51
00:02:54,420 --> 00:02:55,060
Mr. Gao,

52
00:02:55,260 --> 00:02:56,260
you've drunk too much.

53
00:03:00,780 --> 00:03:01,140
Fine.

54
00:03:03,060 --> 00:03:04,900
I'll go to your director tomorrow.

55
00:03:24,900 --> 00:03:25,580
I'm busy now.

56
00:03:26,140 --> 00:03:26,940
Have to hang up.

57
00:03:27,700 --> 00:03:28,100
Bye-bye.

58
00:03:30,380 --> 00:03:31,380
Who were you on the phone with?

59
00:03:31,980 --> 00:03:32,500
A friend.

60
00:03:33,580 --> 00:03:34,540
I've eaten.

61
00:03:36,060 --> 00:03:37,060
Takeout again?

62
00:03:37,380 --> 00:03:39,740
If it continues, your gut may protest.

63
00:03:39,860 --> 00:03:40,940
Guess it's fine.

64
00:03:44,060 --> 00:03:45,500
I heard

65
00:03:46,940 --> 00:03:49,460
you sponsored Siting's school.

66
00:03:52,780 --> 00:03:53,460
Well done,

67
00:03:54,100 --> 00:03:54,820
Wang Zeyuan.

68
00:03:55,580 --> 00:03:56,780
You went all out this time.

69
00:03:57,220 --> 00:03:58,420
What are you talking about?

70
00:03:59,940 --> 00:04:01,140
What am I talking about?

71
00:04:02,860 --> 00:04:05,500
Do you think I'm blind?

72
00:04:06,700 --> 00:04:08,100
Even Bao knows about your secrets.

73
00:04:08,100 --> 00:04:09,060
How could I not know?

74
00:04:09,300 --> 00:04:10,140
After all these years,

75
00:04:10,140 --> 00:04:11,900
I'm clear about what's on your mind.

76
00:04:12,220 --> 00:04:14,420
I like her. What's the problem?

77
00:04:16,020 --> 00:04:16,980
Nothing at all.

78
00:04:17,260 --> 00:04:18,420
We're both single.

79
00:04:18,420 --> 00:04:19,540
No strings attached, no obligations.

80
00:04:19,820 --> 00:04:20,380
Any problem?

81
00:04:22,180 --> 00:04:23,020
No.

82
00:04:27,300 --> 00:04:27,860
Shuhan,

83
00:04:30,540 --> 00:04:32,500
do you think I have a chance

84
00:04:35,500 --> 00:04:36,540
now that she's back?

85
00:04:38,900 --> 00:04:39,940
There is a chance,

86
00:04:41,140 --> 00:04:42,500
but it's quite slim.

87
00:04:43,340 --> 00:04:44,380
After all these years,

88
00:04:44,380 --> 00:04:46,100
you have no sense of reality.

89
00:04:46,100 --> 00:04:47,500
Please stop daydreaming

90
00:04:47,500 --> 00:04:48,540
about Siting.

91
00:04:48,620 --> 00:04:50,020
You know the situation, right?

92
00:04:50,660 --> 00:04:51,220
You...

93
00:04:53,700 --> 00:04:54,820
Don't meddle in my affairs.

94
00:04:55,020 --> 00:04:55,980
As your sister,

95
00:04:55,980 --> 00:04:57,260
I have to look out for you.

96
00:04:57,260 --> 00:04:58,380
I'm an adult now.

97
00:04:58,820 --> 00:05:00,420
Don't want interference.

98
00:05:01,300 --> 00:05:02,540
Besides, I think I'm doing fine.

99
00:05:03,100 --> 00:05:03,820
Thanks for the reminder.

100
00:05:04,860 --> 00:05:05,300
Oh, right,

101
00:05:05,580 --> 00:05:07,220
I'll be going out later.

102
00:05:08,060 --> 00:05:08,940
Should I drop you off?

103
00:05:10,940 --> 00:05:11,460
Alright.

104
00:05:11,980 --> 00:05:13,340
Don't put on the air.

105
00:05:13,940 --> 00:05:14,780
Are you kicking me out?

106
00:05:15,340 --> 00:05:15,860
I'll go.

107
00:05:17,340 --> 00:05:18,860
Make sure you finish all of these later.

108
00:05:18,940 --> 00:05:19,900
I made them myself.

109
00:05:20,260 --> 00:05:21,140
Wash them after you eat.

110
00:05:21,700 --> 00:05:22,540
I won't see you off.

111
00:05:22,980 --> 00:05:23,580
Goodbye.

112
00:05:34,260 --> 00:05:35,300
Yes.

113
00:05:35,300 --> 00:05:35,580
Right.

114
00:05:35,940 --> 00:05:36,220
Yeah.

115
00:05:36,220 --> 00:05:37,100
Need another fifty cases.

116
00:05:37,100 --> 00:05:37,660
Yes.

117
00:05:37,660 --> 00:05:38,380
Cabernet Sauvignon.

118
00:05:38,460 --> 00:05:38,620
Okay.

119
00:05:38,620 --> 00:05:39,020
Is that correct?

120
00:05:39,020 --> 00:05:39,260
Hao,

121
00:05:39,900 --> 00:05:40,940
two extra orders.

122
00:05:40,940 --> 00:05:41,740
See if they were added.

123
00:05:42,540 --> 00:05:43,060
Added?

124
00:05:44,020 --> 00:05:44,580
Let me check.

125
00:05:44,820 --> 00:05:45,100
Okay.

126
00:05:46,300 --> 00:05:46,620
Good.

127
00:05:46,620 --> 00:05:47,580
Thank you.

128
00:05:49,340 --> 00:05:49,900
They've been added.

129
00:05:50,260 --> 00:05:50,820
Sir,

130
00:05:51,060 --> 00:05:53,220
our 2017 vintage wine
is going to sell like hotcakes.

131
00:05:53,980 --> 00:05:55,780
You mentioned having some extra stock.

132
00:05:55,780 --> 00:05:56,500
Is this it?

133
00:05:57,060 --> 00:05:58,340
My phone has been ringing off the hook!

134
00:05:58,340 --> 00:05:59,780
I haven't had a break all morning.

135
00:06:01,260 --> 00:06:02,060
You've worked hard.

136
00:06:02,780 --> 00:06:04,860
Handle all the orders on your hands

137
00:06:05,100 --> 00:06:06,260
and leave work early.

138
00:06:07,860 --> 00:06:08,460
Really?

139
00:06:08,980 --> 00:06:09,820
Thank you.

140
00:06:10,540 --> 00:06:11,900
You're such a kind person.

141
00:06:11,900 --> 00:06:14,340
I was worrying about not watering
the flowers this morning.

142
00:06:15,380 --> 00:06:16,540
If they wither and die,

143
00:06:16,700 --> 00:06:18,540
I would cry my eyes out.

144
00:06:25,660 --> 00:06:26,180
Did you hear that?

145
00:06:26,700 --> 00:06:27,180
What?

146
00:06:30,940 --> 00:06:32,140
She likes flowers.

147
00:06:33,220 --> 00:06:34,060
Likes flowers?

148
00:06:35,420 --> 00:06:36,260
She likes flowers!

149
00:06:36,620 --> 00:06:38,260
But I know nothing about flowers.

150
00:06:38,700 --> 00:06:39,820
After you finish your work,

151
00:06:39,820 --> 00:06:40,700
I'll take you to buy some flowers.

152
00:06:41,020 --> 00:06:41,780
The earlier the better.

153
00:06:42,740 --> 00:06:43,140
Okay.

154
00:06:52,540 --> 00:06:54,540
As a man, take the initiative.

155
00:06:55,060 --> 00:06:56,900
So many flowers. How to choose?

156
00:06:58,140 --> 00:06:58,460
Look.

157
00:06:58,660 --> 00:06:59,900
So many options here.

158
00:07:00,420 --> 00:07:01,700
If you don't know how to choose,

159
00:07:05,020 --> 00:07:05,620
roses

160
00:07:06,380 --> 00:07:07,860
will be the simplest and most direct way

161
00:07:08,140 --> 00:07:10,220
to express your feelings.

162
00:07:10,380 --> 00:07:12,580
That may seem too forward.

163
00:07:13,220 --> 00:07:14,780
Too forward?

164
00:07:14,780 --> 00:07:15,980
Then try the balloon flower.

165
00:07:16,340 --> 00:07:16,900
It's a bit more subtle.

166
00:07:16,900 --> 00:07:17,700
This is the balloon flower?

167
00:07:25,260 --> 00:07:25,620
Madam,

168
00:07:26,420 --> 00:07:27,300
do you sell Velvet?

169
00:07:27,420 --> 00:07:28,420
It's sold out.

170
00:07:28,420 --> 00:07:29,380
Please look somewhere else.

171
00:07:29,940 --> 00:07:30,260
Thank you.

172
00:07:34,540 --> 00:07:34,980
Madam,

173
00:07:35,420 --> 00:07:36,740
do you sell Velvet?

174
00:07:36,780 --> 00:07:37,460
I don't have it.

175
00:07:37,740 --> 00:07:38,700
Turn left ahead.

176
00:07:38,900 --> 00:07:40,020
That shop at the corner should have it.

177
00:07:40,100 --> 00:07:40,660
Go and take a look.

178
00:07:40,740 --> 00:07:41,260
Thanks.

179
00:07:50,580 --> 00:07:50,980
Rui,

180
00:07:51,660 --> 00:07:52,540
what flower is that?

181
00:07:55,060 --> 00:07:55,940
That's

182
00:07:56,740 --> 00:07:57,300
Velvet.

183
00:07:57,860 --> 00:07:58,700
Velvet works too!

184
00:07:58,700 --> 00:08:00,780
A girl would like it
if you give it to her.

185
00:08:02,740 --> 00:08:03,100
Madam.

186
00:08:03,900 --> 00:08:04,580
Please take a look.

187
00:08:04,900 --> 00:08:06,500
Please get me that bunch of Velvet.

188
00:08:10,740 --> 00:08:11,060
Here.

189
00:08:11,260 --> 00:08:11,700
Okay.

190
00:08:14,980 --> 00:08:16,140
This one is indeed prettier.

191
00:08:17,140 --> 00:08:17,900
I'll take this bunch.

192
00:08:18,100 --> 00:08:18,500
Alright.

193
00:08:18,500 --> 00:08:18,780
Okay.

194
00:08:19,580 --> 00:08:20,820
Please scan here.

195
00:08:20,820 --> 00:08:21,100
Okay.

196
00:08:21,100 --> 00:08:21,500
Forty yuan.

197
00:08:21,780 --> 00:08:22,180
Not bad!

198
00:08:22,700 --> 00:08:23,420
This looks nice.

199
00:08:23,580 --> 00:08:24,020
Qi should like it.

200
00:08:24,020 --> 00:08:24,380
Madam,

201
00:08:24,660 --> 00:08:25,860
do you sell Velvet?

202
00:08:27,180 --> 00:08:28,100
Miss, sorry.

203
00:08:28,100 --> 00:08:29,900
The last bunch was sold to them.

204
00:08:30,620 --> 00:08:32,180
If you're not in a hurry,
I can reserve one for you.

205
00:08:35,340 --> 00:08:35,980
That would work.

206
00:08:38,820 --> 00:08:39,340
Madam,

207
00:08:39,860 --> 00:08:41,460
we'd like to change it.

208
00:08:41,740 --> 00:08:42,820
The roses from before.

209
00:08:43,500 --> 00:08:44,220
You want the roses?

210
00:08:44,420 --> 00:08:44,980
We don't want this one.

211
00:08:45,540 --> 00:08:46,220
Thank you.

212
00:08:46,820 --> 00:08:47,260
Then,

213
00:08:47,540 --> 00:08:48,460
this is good.

214
00:08:49,820 --> 00:08:50,340
It's also forty.

215
00:08:50,340 --> 00:08:50,980
Don't need to pay again.

216
00:08:51,180 --> 00:08:51,540
Alright.

217
00:08:51,700 --> 00:08:52,100
Alright.

218
00:08:52,300 --> 00:08:52,900
Thank you!

219
00:08:54,300 --> 00:08:55,500
This one works too!

220
00:08:55,500 --> 00:08:55,860
Velvet.

221
00:08:56,540 --> 00:08:56,740
Okay.

222
00:08:57,180 --> 00:08:58,380
Thank you! How much?

223
00:08:59,020 --> 00:09:00,220
Qi will like this better.

224
00:09:00,420 --> 00:09:00,740
Great.

225
00:09:00,940 --> 00:09:01,220
Okay.

226
00:09:01,220 --> 00:09:01,460
Let's go.

227
00:09:01,740 --> 00:09:01,980
Go.

228
00:09:02,060 --> 00:09:02,660
You can scan here.

229
00:09:02,700 --> 00:09:02,940
Alright.

230
00:09:13,220 --> 00:09:13,580
Rui,

231
00:09:13,940 --> 00:09:14,700
I'll be waiting for you in the car.

232
00:09:23,980 --> 00:09:24,660
What a coincidence.

233
00:09:27,260 --> 00:09:28,940
Never thought that after so many years,

234
00:09:30,140 --> 00:09:31,100
you still like Velvet.

235
00:09:34,380 --> 00:09:35,980
I accompanied a colleague here.

236
00:09:39,700 --> 00:09:42,340
That day, I saw
Peiyan liked Velvet very much,

237
00:09:42,340 --> 00:09:43,820
so I came to get some.

238
00:09:45,100 --> 00:09:46,380
This bunch is for her.

239
00:09:47,060 --> 00:09:48,100
Could you help me

240
00:09:48,820 --> 00:09:49,740
take this back to her?

241
00:09:56,620 --> 00:09:57,460
Let me pay you.

242
00:09:58,100 --> 00:09:58,380
No need.

243
00:09:59,140 --> 00:10:00,300
She and I are colleagues.

244
00:10:00,860 --> 00:10:01,700
No need to be formal.

245
00:10:05,900 --> 00:10:06,300
Alright.

246
00:10:07,260 --> 00:10:08,460
Thank you on behalf of Peiyan.

247
00:10:09,340 --> 00:10:09,820
But

248
00:10:11,380 --> 00:10:12,420
I really think

249
00:10:13,540 --> 00:10:14,780
Velvet would be a very suitable choice

250
00:10:15,860 --> 00:10:17,060
for the bridal bouquet at your wedding.

251
00:10:47,620 --> 00:10:49,580
What brings you here?

252
00:10:50,980 --> 00:10:51,820
This

253
00:10:52,740 --> 00:10:53,340
is for you.

254
00:10:57,780 --> 00:10:58,780
So this is Velvet.

255
00:10:59,540 --> 00:10:59,940
Yes.

256
00:11:02,820 --> 00:11:03,900
Why did you give me flowers

257
00:11:04,300 --> 00:11:05,100
all of a sudden?

258
00:11:07,420 --> 00:11:08,300
Do you still have class?

259
00:11:09,420 --> 00:11:10,300
Yes, one more.

260
00:11:10,780 --> 00:11:12,100
Then go ahead.

261
00:11:15,660 --> 00:11:16,140
Thank you.

262
00:11:16,900 --> 00:11:17,500
I really like it.

263
00:11:19,420 --> 00:11:19,860
I'll head off.

264
00:11:19,900 --> 00:11:20,180
Okay.

265
00:11:29,020 --> 00:11:29,620
Ms. Wen,

266
00:11:31,140 --> 00:11:32,500
how is the wedding preparation going?

267
00:11:33,300 --> 00:11:33,700
Almost there.

268
00:11:34,660 --> 00:11:35,580
You've prepared for so long.

269
00:11:35,580 --> 00:11:37,020
We're looking forward to it.

270
00:11:37,660 --> 00:11:38,340
Once the date is set,

271
00:11:38,380 --> 00:11:39,780
I'll inform you right away.

272
00:11:40,180 --> 00:11:41,380
We have to be there.

273
00:11:42,700 --> 00:11:43,900
These flowers are beautiful.

274
00:11:44,780 --> 00:11:45,300
Thank you.

275
00:11:46,180 --> 00:11:47,380
I'll go back to work.

276
00:11:47,780 --> 00:11:48,420
Okay.

277
00:11:49,940 --> 00:11:51,900
Students in the second row,
see your parents?

278
00:11:51,900 --> 00:11:53,220
Yes!

279
00:11:53,700 --> 00:11:54,420
Go.

280
00:11:55,380 --> 00:11:56,700
Did you say goodbye to your classmates?

281
00:11:56,820 --> 00:11:57,420
Yes!

282
00:11:58,300 --> 00:11:58,820
Off you go.

283
00:11:58,940 --> 00:11:59,660
Take care.

284
00:12:02,540 --> 00:12:03,340
How's the homework load today?

285
00:12:03,660 --> 00:12:04,420
It's okay.

286
00:12:04,420 --> 00:12:04,740
Alright.

287
00:12:04,780 --> 00:12:06,020
Math is a bit tough.

288
00:12:06,060 --> 00:12:07,260
I might need your help.

289
00:12:07,300 --> 00:12:08,380
Helping you is no problem,

290
00:12:08,420 --> 00:12:10,100
but don't have me do all of it for you.

291
00:12:18,140 --> 00:12:19,020
Hello, Lin.

292
00:12:19,380 --> 00:12:20,220
Any orders?

293
00:12:20,500 --> 00:12:21,260
I feel hot.

294
00:12:22,060 --> 00:12:23,260
The air conditioning is on.

295
00:12:25,780 --> 00:12:26,620
Stronger wind.

296
00:12:27,300 --> 00:12:28,180
Don't take this seat.

297
00:12:30,100 --> 00:12:32,180
Dad, you're being so naggy.

