403
00:16:35,940 --> 00:16:36,340
Yes.

404
00:16:36,940 --> 00:16:38,020
One class a week.

405
00:16:43,660 --> 00:16:44,540
She used

406
00:16:45,740 --> 00:16:46,620
to pursue Rui,

407
