428
00:17:46,940 --> 00:17:47,620
No.

429
00:17:48,500 --> 00:17:49,220
Yes.

430
00:17:49,220 --> 00:17:49,820
Definitely!

431
00:17:50,140 --> 00:17:50,460
Hey.

432
00:17:53,540 --> 00:17:55,180
