444
00:18:14,140 --> 00:18:16,300
So I have to consider you

445
00:18:16,500 --> 00:18:17,460
and protect her

446
00:18:17,460 --> 00:18:19,300
from harm.

447
00:18:19,780 --> 00:18:20,900
