they talk about you.

482
00:19:24,820 --> 00:19:26,540
Bad enough when they say it
to our faces,

483
00:19:27,020 --> 00:19:27,780
but behind our backs,

484
00:19:28,260 --> 00:19:29,740
they must be making up stories.

485
00:19:29,740 --> 00:19:30,180
Right?

486
00:19:30,180 --> 00:19:31,580
What did I tell you before?

487
00:19:32,500 --> 00:19:33,500
I asked

488
00:19:33,500 --> 00:19:35,540
you two to move in with me.

489
00:19:36,060 --> 00:19:37,100
If not with me,

490
00:19:37,460 --> 00:19:38,220
live with Yuan.

491
00:19:38,500 --> 00:19:40,060
Where you're living now

492
00:19:40,060 --> 00:19:41,300
