517
00:20:27,500 --> 00:20:28,300
Don't meddle

518
00:20:28,820 --> 00:20:29,380
in our matters.

519
00:20:29,740 --> 00:20:30,700
I really don't want to.

520
00:20:31,700 --> 00:20:32,140
By the way, Mom,

521
00:20:32,780 --> 00:20:33,660
Siting is back.

522
00:20:34,300 --> 00:20:35,100
Siting?

523
00:20:35,580 --> 00:20:36,700
Tan's daughter?

524
00:20:37,060 --> 00:20:37,420
Yeah,

525
00:20:37,820 --> 00:20:38,500
Tan Siting.

526
00:20:39,020 --> 00:20:40,620
We did ballet together
when we were kids.

527
00:20:40,860 --> 00:20:42,020
She went abroad years ago, right?

528
00:20:42,060 --> 00:20:42,540
Yes.

529
00:20:42,700 --> 00:20:43,500
She's back?

530
00:20:43,540 --> 00:20:44,300
Recently.

531
00:20:46,780 --> 00:20:47,860
Does Yuan know?

532
00:20:47,860 --> 00:20:49,580
Of course he knows.

533
00:20:49,580 --> 00:20:50,620
Not only does he know,

534
00:20:50,980 --> 00:20:52,180
