538
00:20:58,780 --> 00:20:59,260
Besides,

539
00:20:59,460 --> 00:21:00,820
Siting is doing well now.

540
00:21:01,260 --> 00:21:03,100
She's a teacher at a ballet school.

541
00:21:03,540 --> 00:21:05,820
Yuan even sponsored her

542
00:21:06,100 --> 00:21:07,660
to support her career.

543
00:21:08,540 --> 00:21:09,180
Sponsored her?

544
00:21:12,100 --> 00:21:12,540
Dad,

545
00:21:13,460 --> 00:21:15,580
I always make mistakes
with triangle calculations.

546
00:21:17,060 --> 00:21:17,580
Which one?

547
00:21:18,100 --> 00:21:18,500
This one.

548
00:21:18,700 --> 00:21:19,420
This one, yes.

549
00:21:20,260 --> 00:21:20,940
Calculate it like this.

550
00:21:22,020 --> 00:21:22,860
These two sides,

551
00:21:23,580 --> 00:21:25,060
AE over PA

552
00:21:25,300 --> 00:21:26,420
equals three times ten.

553
00:21:26,460 --> 00:21:27,380
Equals one-half.

554
00:21:27,700 --> 00:21:28,260
Then,

555
00:21:28,300 --> 00:21:29,500
the sine of AF is

556
00:21:29,540 --> 00:21:31,580
AF over PA,

557
00:21:32,540 --> 00:21:33,980
which equals sine sixty degrees,

558
00:21:34,020 --> 00:21:35,220
and that's one-half

559
00:21:35,860 --> 00:21:36,780
root three.

560
00:21:37,780 --> 00:21:39,060
Alright, so AF equals

561
00:21:39,260 --> 00:21:41,260
