562
00:21:42,820 --> 00:21:43,260
There we go.

563
00:21:44,060 --> 00:21:44,500
Now look.

564
00:21:49,060 --> 00:21:49,500
Wait.

565
00:21:50,460 --> 00:21:51,580
What are

566
00:21:52,460 --> 00:21:53,980
trigonometric function formulas?

567
00:21:54,540 --> 00:21:55,820
Haven't you

568
00:21:56,060 --> 00:21:56,700
learned them yet?

569
00:21:58,060 --> 00:21:59,260
Never heard of them.

570
00:21:59,860 --> 00:22:01,580
That's beyond my level.

571
00:22:02,700 --> 00:22:03,420
Haven't heard of it?

572
00:22:05,740 --> 00:22:09,180
We won't learn that

573
00:22:09,740 --> 00:22:10,260
