574
00:22:10,300 --> 00:22:10,820
Haven't learned?

575
00:22:11,020 --> 00:22:12,260
I'm only in Grade six.

576
00:22:15,260 --> 00:22:15,860
I remember

577
00:22:15,860 --> 00:22:17,980
